<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Van Huihchim!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van huihchim, ka hun ngai ie hung lengin,
 Ka suihlunga meipi zing mut thielin;
 Thim leh lungngaihna hin kei ei nanga,
 Ka zawt lai kumsawt pielgal a lieh hi.

[V2]
 Lalpa bangkima kei dinga Bangkim,
 Hinna khuktui Na hi, ka hun ngai hi;
 Lopina leh van mun ka ngai chuom puoi,
 Van chu Nang Na hi, naubang ei dawnin

[V3]
 2. Tuona Eden pak tana lengsa nung.
 Albang I vai sietlei gitloh thimah;
 Mahleh Kalvari a ngabang leng te,
 Kumsawt gam Eden thak nuom khun a sam.

[V4]
 3. Simlei pakcha lun hawih cheng a hung vuoi,
 A nawplau leh gi hawih tin cheng a dai;
 Lal deihum Na sakmel a tuoi thei puoi,
 Naubang ei nem ie kumsawt chan inle.

[V5]
 4. Na min theibang ka lawh tieng thim a bei,
 Sietlei gam lunghel um zailan ka awi;
 Nunnawp puon bang thak zel ka gen seng puoi,
 Na engin kei di'n taikhuo a vak ie.</lyrics>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>113</hymn_number>
</song>